    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using Beta5's escapeHtml or escapeHtmlAttr helpers, the preg_match() function fails with the following error message.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
preg_match(): Compilation failed: unknown option bit(s) set at offset 0 in /var/www/html/vendor/zendframework/zendframework/library/Zend/Escaper/Escaper.php on line 349
</code></pre>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
Line 349: } elseif (preg_match('/^./su', $string) == 1) {
</code></pre>

<p>The server is running with PCRE version 7.8 with UTF-8 &amp; Unicode support on.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
